## API

### Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|------|
| `modelValue` | `(string \| number)[]` | `[]` | TextValue（Text） |
| `columns` | `PickerColumn[]` | `[]` | Description for columns. |
| `visible` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for visible. |
| `popup` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for popup. |
| `title` | `string` | `''` | Description for title. |
| `showToolbar` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for showToolbar. |
| `confirmText` | `string` | `'Confirm'` | Description for confirmText. |
| `cancelText` | `string` | `'Cancel'` | Description for cancelText. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for disabled. |
| `itemHeight` | `number` | `36` | Description for itemHeight. |
| `visibleItemCount` | `number` | `5` | Description for visibleItemCount. |
| `closeOnClickMask` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for closeOnClickMask. |
| `lazyMount` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for lazyMount. |

### PickerColumn

| Field | Type | Description |
|------|------|------|
| `key` | `string` | Description for key. |
| `options` | `PickerOption[]` | Description for options. |

### PickerOption

| Field | Type | Description |
|------|------|------|
| `value` | `string \| number` | Value |
| `label` | `string` | Description for label. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | Description for disabled. |

